description:
Pedunculate oak - Tree 347 of survey (not TPO).  Reduce spread of lowest half of the tree's crown on its southern side by 2 metres, ensuring that 2 metres' clearance between branch tips and building is achieved.  Reduce length of low branch directly opposite first floor window of 19 Heronsforde by 2-3 metres.  
Reason:  To reduce the nuisance caused by the tree's crown which is currently very close to, and almost touching the building.
